  "intro": "The Judy Robe & Spirit Awards are an important part of every PYT Main Stage production. Presented just before opening night, they celebrate and recognise cast members whose dedication, generosity, and spirit make our shows great. The Judy Robe Award goes to the ensemble member who best embodies the values of our long term supporter and volunteer Judy Meyer. Spirit Awards go to three or four performers each show, who have represented PYT's values of braveness, responsibility, and kindness throughout the production run.",
